## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="e1a72-151">此实现<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter>非常有用的应用程序必须调用中`Fill`为两个或多个方法<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter>对象。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e1a72-151">This implementation of the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter> can be useful in an application that must call the `Fill` method for two or more <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter> objects.</span></span>  
  
   
  
