## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="e1a72-207">当<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.SelectCommand%2A>分配到以前创建<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand>，则<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand>不克隆。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e1a72-207">When <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.SelectCommand%2A> is assigned to a previously created <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand>, the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand> is not cloned.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="e1a72-208">相反，<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.SelectCommand%2A>保留对以前创建的引用<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand>对象。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e1a72-208">Instead, the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.SelectCommand%2A> maintains a reference to the previously created <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand> object.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="e1a72-209">如果<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.SelectCommand%2A>不返回任何行的表添加到**数据集**，并不会引发异常。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e1a72-209">If <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.SelectCommand%2A> does not return any rows, no tables are added to the **DataSet**, and no exception is raised.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="e1a72-210">下面的示例创建<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter>，并设置<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.SelectCommand%2A>和<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.InsertCommand%2A>属性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e1a72-210">The following example creates an <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter> and sets the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.SelectCommand%2A> and <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.InsertCommand%2A> properties.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="e1a72-211">它假定你已创建<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleConnection>对象。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e1a72-211">It assumes you have already created an <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleConnection> object.</span></span>  
  
```vb  
Public Shared Function CreateCustomerAdapter(conn As OracleConnection) As OracleDataAdapter   
  
  Dim da As OracleDataAdapter = New OracleDataAdapter()  
  Dim cmd As OracleCommand  
  
  ' Create the SelectCommand.  
  
  cmd = New OracleCommand("SELECT * FROM Dept " & _  
                       "WHERE DName = :pDName AND Loc = :pLoc", conn)  
  
  cmd.Parameters.Add("pDName", OracleType.NVarChar, 14)  
  cmd.Parameters.Add("pLoc", OracleType.NVarChar, 13)  
  
  da.SelectCommand = cmd  
  
  ' Create the InsertCommand.  
  
  cmd = New OracleCommand("INSERT INTO Dept (DeptNo, DName) " & _  
                       "VALUES (pDeptNo, pDName)", conn)  
  
  cmd.Parameters.Add("pDeptNo", OracleType.Number, 2, "DeptNo")  
  cmd.Parameters.Add("pDName", OracleType.NVarChar, 14, "DName")  
  
  da.InsertCommand = cmd  
  
  Return da  
End Function  
```  
  
```csharp  
public static OracleDataAdapter CreateCustomerAdapter(OracleConnection conn)  
{  
  OracleDataAdapter da = new OracleDataAdapter();  
  OracleCommand cmd;  
  
  // Create the SelectCommand.  
  
  cmd = new OracleCommand("SELECT * FROM Dept " +  
                       "WHERE DName = :pDName AND Loc = :pLoc", conn);  
  
  cmd.Parameters.Add("pDName", OracleType.NVarChar, 14);  
  cmd.Parameters.Add("pLoc", OracleType.NVarChar, 13);  
  
  da.SelectCommand = cmd;  
  
  // Create the InsertCommand.  
  
  cmd = new OracleCommand("INSERT INTO Dept (DeptNo, DName) " +  
                       "VALUES (:pDeptNo, :pDName)", conn);  
  
  cmd.Parameters.Add("pDeptNo", OracleType.Number, 2, "DeptNo");  
  cmd.Parameters.Add("pDName", OracleType.NVarChar, 14, "DName");  
  
  da.InsertCommand = cmd;  
  
  return da;  
}  
```

  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="e1a72-253">当<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.UpdateCommand%2A>分配到以前创建<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand>，则<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand>不克隆。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e1a72-253">When <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.UpdateCommand%2A> is assigned to a previously created <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand>, the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand> is not cloned.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="e1a72-254">相反，<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.UpdateCommand%2A>保留对以前创建的引用<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand>对象。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e1a72-254">Instead, the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.UpdateCommand%2A> maintains a reference to the previously created <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand> object.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="e1a72-255">更新操作期间，如果<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.InsertCommand%2A>未设置主键中存在信息时**数据集**，可以使用<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommandBuilder>类，以自动生成<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.InsertCommand%2A>，和所需的其他命令对帐<xref:System.Data.DataSet>到数据库。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e1a72-255">During an update operation, if <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.InsertCommand%2A> is not set and primary key information is present in the **DataSet**, you can use the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommandBuilder> class to automatically generate <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.InsertCommand%2A>, and additional commands needed to reconcile the <xref:System.Data.DataSet> to the database.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="e1a72-256">若要执行此操作，设置<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.SelectCommand%2A>属性的<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter>。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e1a72-256">To do this, set the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.SelectCommand%2A> property of the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="e1a72-257">生成逻辑还要求要中存在的键列信息<xref:System.Data.DataSet>。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e1a72-257">The generation logic also requires key column information to be present in the <xref:System.Data.DataSet>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="e1a72-258">有关详细信息请参阅[使用 Commandbuilder 生成命令](~/docs/framework/data/adonet/generating-commands-with-commandbuilders.md)。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e1a72-258">For more information see [Generating Commands with CommandBuilders](~/docs/framework/data/adonet/generating-commands-with-commandbuilders.md).</span></span>  
  
> [!NOTE]
>  <span data-ttu-id="e1a72-259">如果执行此命令返回的行，这些行可能会与合并<xref:System.Data.DataSet>取决于如何设置<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand.UpdatedRowSource%2A>属性的<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand>对象。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e1a72-259">If execution of this command returns rows, these rows may be merged with the <xref:System.Data.DataSet> depending upon how you set the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand.UpdatedRowSource%2A> property of the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand> object.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="e1a72-260">当您更新的列`LONG RAW`数据类型，将引发异常时输入的值为`NULL`列中。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e1a72-260">When you update a column with the `LONG RAW` data type, an exception is thrown when you enter a value of `NULL` in the column.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="e1a72-261">Oracle`LONG RAW`数据类型为 Oracle 版本 8.0 中的不推荐使用的类型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e1a72-261">The Oracle `LONG RAW` data type is a deprecated type in Oracle version 8.0.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="e1a72-262">若要避免此错误，请使用`BLOB`数据类型而非`LONG RAW`。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e1a72-262">To avoid this error, use the `BLOB` data type instead of `LONG RAW`.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="e1a72-263">下面的示例创建<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter>，并设置<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.SelectCommand%2A>和<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.UpdateCommand%2A>属性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e1a72-263">The following example creates an <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter> and sets the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.SelectCommand%2A> and <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.UpdateCommand%2A> properties.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="e1a72-264">它假定你已创建<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleConnection>对象。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e1a72-264">It assumes you have already created an <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleConnection> object.</span></span>  
  
```vb  
Public Shared Function CreateCustomerAdapter(conn As OracleConnection) As OracleDataAdapter   
  
  Dim da As OracleDataAdapter = New OracleDataAdapter()  
  Dim cmd As OracleCommand  
  Dim parm As OracleParameter  
  
  ' Create the SelectCommand.  
  
  cmd = New OracleCommand("SELECT * FROM Dept " & _  
                       "WHERE DName = pDName AND Loc = pLoc", conn)  
  
  cmd.Parameters.Add("pDName", OracleType.NVarChar, 14)  
  cmd.Parameters.Add("pLoc", OracleType.NVarChar, 13)  
  
  da.SelectCommand = cmd  
  
  ' Create the UpdateCommand.  
  
  cmd = New OracleCommand("UPDATE Dept SET DeptNo = pDeptNo, DName = pDName " & _  
                       "WHERE DeptNo = poldDeptNo", conn)  
  
  cmd.Parameters.Add("pDeptNo", OracleType.Number, 2, "DeptNo")  
  cmd.Parameters.Add("pDName", OracleType.NVarChar, 14, "DName")  
  
  parm = cmd.Parameters.Add("poldDeptNo", OracleType.Number, 2, "DeptNo")  
  parm.SourceVersion = DataRowVersion.Original  
  
  da.UpdateCommand = cmd  
  
  Return da  
End Function  
```  
  
```csharp  
public static OracleDataAdapter CreateCustomerAdapter(OracleConnection conn)  
{  
  OracleDataAdapter da = new OracleDataAdapter();  
  OracleCommand cmd;  
  OracleParameter parm;  
  
  // Create the SelectCommand.  
  
  cmd = new OracleCommand("SELECT * FROM Dept " +  
                       "WHERE DName = pDName AND Loc = pLoc", conn);  
  
  cmd.Parameters.Add("pDName", OracleType.NVarChar, 14);  
  cmd.Parameters.Add("pLoc", OracleType.NVarChar, 13);  
  
  da.SelectCommand = cmd;  
  
  // Create the UpdateCommand.  
  
  cmd = new OracleCommand("UPDATE Dept SET DeptNo = pDeptNo, DName = pDName " +  
                       "WHERE DeptNo = poldDeptNo", conn);  
  
  cmd.Parameters.Add("pDeptNo", OracleType.Number, 2, "DeptNo");  
  cmd.Parameters.Add("pDName", OracleType.NVarChar, 14, "DName");  
  
  parm = cmd.Parameters.Add("poldDeptNo", OracleType.Number, 2, "DeptNo");  
  parm.SourceVersion = DataRowVersion.Original;  
  
  da.UpdateCommand = cmd;  
  
  return da;  
}  
```
